    ROLE -->|Yes| MAP[Map role -> EApp flags]
    MAP --> HASOPP{oppID provided?}
    HASOPP -->|No| BUILD[Build SoReqData]
    HASOPP -->|Yes| QOPP[Query opportunity + contact]
    QOPP --> BUILD
